title: Diane discusses the impact of the model minority myth

media:group.media:title: Diane discusses the impact of the model minority myth
media:group.media:description:
Diane, a “Being Asian in America” documentary participant, discusses the impact of the model minority myth and the effect it’s had on her self-esteem.

This video is part of our “Being Asian in America” project. 
Watch the full documentary here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LIIvqJDv6_4 
For more on the project, visit https://www.pewresearch.org/BeingAsianInAmerica
